            <title>[LU-6638] sanity-hsm test_37:request on 0x200000401:0x2d:0x0 is not SUCCEED on mds1</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-6638</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for wangdi &amp;lt;di.wang@intel.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/85dc64f0-0255-11e5-9636-5254006e85c2&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/85dc64f0-0255-11e5-9636-5254006e85c2&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The sub-test test_37 failed with the following error:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;request on 0x200000401:0x2d:0x0 is not SUCCEED on mds1
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Although I only saw this failure during DNE2 test, but I can not see this failure is related with the patch. Let&apos;s see if this is repeatable. &lt;/p&gt;

